NOTE ON DATA LICENSING

This license applies to the SOURCE CODE in this repository only. Data products
in `data/` have varying licensing terms and are documented separately in
`docs/data_attribution.md`. In particular:

  - Raw EconLit exports under `data/EconLit/` are licensed by EBSCO and
    cannot be redistributed. They are excluded from this repository via
    `.gitignore` and must be obtained by replicators directly through their
    institutional library subscription. The procedure is documented in
    `docs/econlit_export_instructions.md`.

  - Derived data products under `data/` (final_dataset.csv,
    summary_journal_year.csv, jel_lookup.csv, lmic_countries.csv) are
    released under CC-BY-4.0 with attribution to underlying sources
    (OpenAlex, Crossref, Semantic Scholar, the AEA, and the World Bank).
